          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"the-refusal-axis-in-domain-space\">The Refusal Axis in Domain Space</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Interactive exploration of refusal geometry in Gemma 3 12B.\nExtends the Assistant Axis methodology (Lu et al. 2026) to refusal behavior,\ndecomposing a single refusal direction into per-domain sub-directions.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Key finding:</strong> \"I won't\" (value-based refusal) and \"I can't\" (capability boundary)\nare geometrically near-orthogonal \u2014 different mechanisms, independently controllable.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
